          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/41892251-love-lies">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2847111338" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11353621379657223502"><strong>Sad, tragic true crime</strong><br/><br/>I read a lot of true crime books and many of them really fascinate me as well as make me feel such sympathy for the family of the victim. This book truly touched my heart. The author, who is new to me, truly details the family of the victim, including her two daughters, her twin sister, parents, brother and little sister and the emotional ups and downs they went through. This book truly captured the emotional impact on a victim&apos;s family and is exceptional in that aspect. Th</span>
  <span id="freeText11353621379657223502" style="display:none"><strong>Sad, tragic true crime</strong><br /><br />I read a lot of true crime books and many of them really fascinate me as well as make me feel such sympathy for the family of the victim. This book truly touched my heart. The author, who is new to me, truly details the family of the victim, including her two daughters, her twin sister, parents, brother and little sister and the emotional ups and downs they went through. This book truly captured the emotional impact on a victim's family and is exceptional in that aspect. This is an outstanding true crime book and I highly recommend it to all true crime readers.</span>
